In this set of notes, you will learn another method of dealing with nonlinearity and also for dealing with heterogeneity of variance. Specifically, we will look at log-transforming the predictor in a linear model. To do so, we will use the movies.csv dataset (see the data codebook) to explain variation in movie budgets.
